OL,3,CPip and universal credit cuts: Who
OL,4,Cwill be hit and how much will they
OL,5,Close?
OL,7,FSince the government's planned welfare
OL,8,Fcuts were first announced in March,
OL,9,Fconcern among disabled people,
OL,10,Fcharities, and backbench MPs has
OL,11,Fcontinued to grow.
OL,13,FThe outcry in response to the reforms
OL,14,Fhas plagued Sir Keir Starmer and his
OL,15,Fministers as they seek to win over
OL,16,FLabour MPs on the changes.
OL,18,FDespite more than 120 Labour MPs
OL,19,Fbacking a move to block the
OL,20,Flegislation, the government insists it
OL,21,Fis pressing ahead with the reforms.
