OL,3,CPip and universal credit cuts: Who
OL,4,Cwill be hit and how much will they
OL,5,Close?
OL,7,FPersonal Independence Payment (Pip) is
OL,8,Fpaid to support people with a long
OL,9,Fterm physical or mental health
OL,10,Fcondition or disability.
OL,12,FIt's not connected to whether or not
OL,13,Fyou can work, and is designed to cover
OL,14,Fthe additional costs associated with
OL,15,Fbeing disabled or long-term sick.
OL,17,FThere are current 3.7 million people
OL,18,Fclaiming Pip, and under the
OL,19,Fgovernment's changes it's estimated
OL,20,Fthe cuts will affect around 800,000
OL,21,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
