OL,3,CPip and universal credit cuts: Who
OL,4,Cwill be hit and how much will they
OL,5,Close?
OL,7,FThere are two parts to Pip - the daily
OL,8,Fliving component, and the mobility
OL,9,Fcomponent. The mobility component is
OL,10,Fnot affected by the changes, but the
OL,11,Fgovernment is making it more difficult
OL,12,Ffor people to claim the daily living
OL,13,Fcomponent by tightening eligibility.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
