OL,3,CPip and universal credit cuts: Who
OL,4,Cwill be hit and how much will they
OL,5,Close?
OL,7,FPeople are assessed for Pip through
OL,8,Fquestions about their ability to do
OL,9,Fdifferent daily tasks independently,
OL,10,Fwith each task scaled on a scale from
OL,11,Fzero to twelve. They currently need to
OL,12,Fscore eight points across the
OL,13,Fdifferent categories for the standard
OL,14,Frate, or twelve for the higher rate.
OL,16,FBut under the new plans, from November
OL,17,F2026 claimants will need to score at
OL,18,Fleast four points for one activity,
OL,19,Frather than a lower number of points
OL,20,Facross multiple activities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
