OL,3,CPip and universal credit cuts: Who
OL,4,Cwill be hit and how much will they
OL,5,Close?
OL,7,FThe Universal Credit and Personal
OL,8,FIndependence Payment Bill also says
OL,9,Fthat there will be a 13 week
OL,10,Ftransition period for anyone losing
OL,11,Ftheir Pip, instead of the standard
OL,12,Ffour weeks.
OL,14,FWhat are the changes to universal
OL,15,Fcredit and how many will be hit?
OL,17,FUniversal credit (UC) is a monthly
OL,18,Fbenefit paid to those who need extra
OL,19,Fsupport with living and housing costs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
