OL,3,CPip and universal credit cuts: Who
OL,4,Cwill be hit and how much will they
OL,5,Close?
OL,7,FSingle claimants over 25 get #400.14 a
OL,8,Fmonth on the basic rate, but people
OL,9,Fwith a limited capacity to work,
OL,10,Fbecause of a disability or long term
OL,11,Fsickness, get an additional top-up of
OL,12,F#416.19.
OL,14,FUnder the government's reforms, the UC
OL,15,Fhealth top-up for new claimants will
OL,16,Fbe cut in half from #97 a week to #50
OL,17,Fa week in 2026-7, and will then be
OL,18,Ffrozen until 2030.
OL,20,FExisting claimants will also have the
OL,21,Fincapacity top-up frozen until 2030.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
