OL,3,CPip and universal credit cuts: Who
OL,4,Cwill be hit and how much will they
OL,5,Close?
OL,7,FWhile the top-up is being cut for new
OL,8,Fclaimants, the basic rate of universal
OL,9,Fcredit will rise from around #92 a
OL,10,Fweek to #106 a week by 2030.
OL,12,FHow many people will be hit?
OL,14,FThe government's own estimates say 3.2
OL,15,Ffamilies will be financially impacted
OL,16,Fby the cuts, with an average loss of
OL,17,F#1,720 a year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
