OL,3,CPip and universal credit cuts: Who
OL,4,Cwill be hit and how much will they
OL,5,Close?
OL,7,FHow much will the cuts save?
OL,9,FThe welfare bill has ballooned in
OL,10,Frecent years, with the government
OL,11,Fspending #65 billion a year on health
OL,12,Fand disability benefits. Before the
OL,13,Fgovernment's reforms, the bill was set
OL,14,Fto rise to #100 billion by 2030.
OL,16,FThe cost of the Pip bill alone was due
OL,17,Fto almost double to #34 billion by
OL,18,F2030.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
