OL,4,Cwill be hit and how much will they
OL,5,Close?
OL,7,FThe total package is expected to save
OL,8,Fthe government #5 billion a year by
OL,9,F2030.
OL,11,FOne in 10 working age people now claim
OL,12,Fsickness or disability benefit, and 1
OL,13,Fmillion young people are not in
OL,14,Feducation, work or training.
OL,16,FWork and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,17,FKendall has previously said there are
OL,18,F1,000 new Pip awards every day ` "the
OL,19,Fequivalent of adding a city the size
OL,20,Fof Leicester every single year".
