OL,7,FHow many MPs are opposing the plans?
OL,9,FFor months Labour MPs have been
OL,10,Fvoicing anger at the plans both
OL,11,Fpublicly and privately, but this week
OL,12,Fover 120 have signed a reasoned
OL,13,Famendment to the bill which could
OL,14,Fthreaten to derail the plans.
OL,16,FThere are also 11 MPs from other
OL,17,Fparties backing the amendment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
